1
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:41,880
Wait a minute.

2
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,010
I have a gift for you.

3
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:55,360
Today

4
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:57,480
is your 18th birthday.

5
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:59,840
Ever since your mom remarried,

6
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:03,890
I made you live in the room furthest from mine.

7
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:05,440
And having you call me Brother Angwei

8
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:08,240
wasn't because I really wanted to be your brother.

9
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:09,520
It's just that

10
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,240
I was afraid

11
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,560
being too close to you,

12
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:15,080
I would cross the line.

13
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:19,920
But after spending all this time together,

14
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:21,520
I am sure.

15
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,880
I want to protect you.

16
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:27,580
Because every time I see you unhappy,

17
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:28,690
I just...

18
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,200
I panic.

19
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,240
And when

20
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,920
I see you being wronged,

21
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,780
it makes me feel

22
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,320
worse than my own unhappiness,

23
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:40,320
a thousand, a million times worse.

24
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:43,800
So,

25
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,400
I always thought

26
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,320
you only saw me as a sister.

27
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,800
How is that possible?

28
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:51,360
I swear,

29
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:54,039
I will never let you suffer

30
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:54,880
or be bullied.

31
00:01:59,479 --> 00:02:00,280
I know.

32
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,600
From now on,

33
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:06,040
let me celebrate your birthday with you every year, okay?

34
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,400
You said it yourself.

35
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,860
Every year on my birthday,

36
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,600
you must be by my side.

37
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:13,480
I swear. If I'm not,

38
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,000
may lightning strike me.

39
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:18,810
As long as you remember.

40
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,040
Blow the candles.

41
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,600
I didn't do anything to you.

42
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,800
You're awake.

43
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,300
What happened?

44
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,060
Does your head still hurt?

45
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:18,680
Here is the test report for that glass of wine from yesterday.

46
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:22,480
Hallucinogens.

47
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,450
Your condition just now

48
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,920
was very similar to mine five years ago.

49
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,329
So I sent someone

50
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,700
to test that glass of wine.

51
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,890
Sure enough,

52
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,700
it contained hallucinogens.

53
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,600
So...

54
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:47,280
I'm sorry.

55
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:52,840
It's okay.

56
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,680
This was all Ruannila's doing.

57
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:02,960
Dailing.

58
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:05,450
Don't worry.

59
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,680
I will kill her.

60
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,780
Did you sleep well last night?

61
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,260
Why did you get up so early?

62
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,600
Did I wake you up?

63
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,560
Not really.

64
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:05,160
I felt a gaze

65
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,040
coveting my beauty.

66
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,320
What beauty?

67
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:16,400
Do I?

68
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,170
A little bit.

69
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:34,640
Why do I feel like all of this

70
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,200
is like a dream?

71
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:42,659
I wouldn't even dare to have such a luxurious dream.

72
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,200
Over the past five years,

73
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,850
I either dreamed of you calling for help in the sea

74
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:54,380
or getting further and further away from me.

75
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:57,720
I couldn't catch up no matter how hard I chased.

76
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:08,960
Lingling.

77
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:16,280
You can't leave me again.

78
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,040
If you leave me again,

79
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,400
I'll die too.

80
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,400
I won't leave you again.

81
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,960
We just need to keep holding hands like this,

82
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,090
holding on forever.

83
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,730
How come I never noticed before

84
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:49,040
that you're so childish?

85
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,610
It's not childishness.

86
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,240
It's fear.

87
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:09,920
Right.

88
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,970
That poisonous snake Ruannila

89
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,780
should have died long ago.

90
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,490
Otherwise, she will

91
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,050
keep bothering you.

92
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,800
I'm afraid she will hurt you.

93
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,700
But we have no proof right now.

94
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,650
We shouldn't rush this.

95
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,820
I have found a way to deal with her.

96
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:38,240
I've collected some things.

97
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,280
I thought

98
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,530
you should definitely take a look.

99
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,600
Over the years, Ruannila

100
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,000
used your name

101
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,280
to embezzle these corporate funds.

102
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,610
Did you know about this?

103
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,659
Would she dare?

104
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:55,290
Of the group's revenue,

105
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:58,120
she takes forty percent every year.

106
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,540
Isn't her appetite

107
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,080
a bit too big?

108
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,720
This bitch

109
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,440
is so audacious.

110
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:09,920
Also...

111
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:11,120
What else?

112
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,920
She is also

113
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,920
keeping many men on the side.

114
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,980
College students,

115
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,520
male models.

116
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,960
Rumor has it that Lapeng

117
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,220
used to be with her too.

118
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,440
This woman

119
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:24,840
financially

120
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,010
betrayed the group,

121
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:29,130
and emotionally betrayed you.

122
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,080
This woman

123
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,210
is just ungrateful.

124
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,039
Father.

125
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,000
Moreover,

126
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:39,480
the media already has their eyes on her.

127
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:41,039
But don't worry, Father.

128
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,640
I have blocked the news.

129
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,240
I just feel that if this news gets out,

130
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,560
our Sihai Group

131
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,690
will be humiliated in all of Mancheng.

132
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:00,840
Angwei,

133
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,520
Women...

134
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,880
Harmony in the family leads to prosperity.

135
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,130
Sir, I was wrong.

136
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,720
Sir, I was wrong.

137
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,080
I made you the lady of the house

138
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,080
to manage it well.

139
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,890
Did you forget where you came from?

140
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,520
I didn't, sir.

141
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,000
I know I was wrong.

142
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,080
You gave me everything I have.

143
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,810
You know I gave you everything.

144
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:31,000
Yet you stole company money.

145
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,720
How dare you!

146
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,240
Master,

147
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,040
I didn't.

148
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:36,320
Using my money to keep a lover.

149
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,480
Are you happy?

150
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,680
Did you enjoy it?

151
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,920
Master, stop hitting me.

152
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:40,580
I was wrong.

153
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:41,880
I know I was wrong.

154
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,040
I didn't. I didn't.

155
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:44,760
I am just your dog.

156
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,290
Please spare me.

157
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,060
Master,

158
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,180
she is here.

159
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,080
Stay put.

160
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:54,600
It's Hua.

161
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,580
Master.

162
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:58,920
It was Hua.

163
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,400
Hua saved Dailing.

164
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,440
She put Dailing with the mercenaries

165
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,170
and trained her for five years.

166
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,760
The one who betrayed you is Hua.

167
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,620
Stay on your knees.

168
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:14,900
I'll deal with you when I get back.

169
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,560
Dailing,

170
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,880
it's all because of you.

171
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,520
I'm going to kill you.
